schools.name: Bonita Springs Middle Center For The Arts

data.description: Amazing opportunity in the heart of Bonita Springs. Meticulously maintained 3 bedroom and 2 bath. Newer construction in 2018. Amazing family home minutes from local attractions, beaches, fine dining and best of all 20 miles from South West International Airport. 2 car garage that is under air conditioning. Roof straps, hurricane shutters up to code as of 2018. HVAC serviced regularly. Interior newly painted/exterior painted 1 year ago. Quiet neighborhood with a progressive arts center across the street. Total Backyard Privacy Fence along with convenient total yard Irrigation throughout...Much to do and see in the heart of Bonita Springs.
